@sathyaprakashg : Thanks for catching this.
Yes, this method should not be there in the first place.
Though, For context, this is innocuous as Hudi uses the property hoodie.compact.inline.max.delta.commits for figure out inline compaction interval. The associated set API  is withMaxNumDeltaCommitsBeforeCompaction()(https://hudi.apache.org/docs/configurations.html#withMaxNumDeltaCommitsBeforeCompaction). Can you try setting this value : hoodie.compact.inline.max.delta.commits to a higher value ?

